rComments: I don't think she knows how to teach. All she does is read off slides that she didn't even create herself, and she reads them in monotone. Not surprised as to why nobody attends class.
Her lectures might be boring to many people, but she's really kind during the office hours. Gives good feedback and willing to help student out.
One of the most empathetic prof at uoft. Even when i messed up me essay topic she gave me a chance so i dont have to rewrite another one. Can not believe there are professor this kind at Uoft
